{"type": "article", "id": 2224, "title": "索尼微单 Alpha 5100", "description": "", "date": "2014-09-07T23:02:13Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 2, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 5, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605222257ovRfulOCnc4eK3ME.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">日前，索尼正式发布了一款外形时尚靓丽的全新微单 Alpha 5100，也可以被看做是 Nex-5T 的升级版本。这款新品号称是全球最小巧搭载内闪的  APS-C 相机，最大卖点在于其升级的对焦系统和视频拍摄功能，采用的是 2430 万像素 APS-C 画幅搭配 BIONZ X 处理器的 Exmor COMS 传感器，最高连拍 6 张/秒，最高快门速度 1/4000 秒。真皮包覆的手柄很有质感，还有 180 度反转自拍功能，套机 4499 元，预计将于 9 月正式上市，</span><a href=\"http://www.sonystyle.com.cn/products/nex/ilce_5100/ilce_5100_promo.htm\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里抢先预订</a><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135107O0Wa7m5GeviPxwdK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135108gOz28dACnvlyP6Z0.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"340\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.53142857\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/2016072613510987BXkoCJq4OftTZQ.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"412\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.64333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135109dMaUbI5r90spEClT.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7046875\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}